node.text:
LOOK AT THIS. Congrats to @ronnieradke first of all for recreating one of his old songs into this masterpiece and for letting me be apart of it, people are seeing how amazingly talented you are 🥺 big congrats and thank you to @jensennoen for the direction. You and ronnie together are a powerful force in this industry. 
The whole team on the set were incredible and so fun to work with. GO WATCH MY OSCAR WINNING PERFORMANCE. Also swipe for a good time....
